PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Blockchain Analytics Platform
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Blockchain analytics involves parsing and analyzing data from blockchain networks to gain insights into transaction patterns, network activity, and potential security risks or fraudulent behavior.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our platform connects to various blockchain networks and ingests their data in real-time. We then apply advanced analytics techniques to extract meaningful information and visualizations for our users.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We currently support analysis for Bitcoin, Ethereum, and several other major blockchain networks. Our platform is designed to be blockchain-agnostic and can be extended to new networks.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Who can benefit from using your analytics platform?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our platform is valuable for blockchain companies, financial institutions, investigators, and researchers seeking insights from blockchain data for AML, security, or analytical purposes.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our blockchain data analysis app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Blockchain data analysis refers to the process of extracting, processing and interpreting data from blockchain networks. Our app provides tools to query, filter and visualize blockchain data to gain insights.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What blockchains does your app support?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our app currently supports analysis of data from Bitcoin, Ethereum, and several other major blockchains. We are continuously working on adding support for more networks.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We maintain our own nodes on the blockchain networks to directly source the latest data as it gets added to the chains. This ensures data integrity and real-time analysis capabilities.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I analyze private/permissioned blockchain data?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, our enterprise plans allow you to ingest and analyze data from your own private or permissioned blockchain networks hosted on premises or in the cloud.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What analysis capabilities does the app offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: The app provides features like transaction monitoring, address tracking, token analysis, smart contract analysis, chain metrics and customizable dashboards to visualize insights.
